WEBVTT

00:02.344 --> 00:06.445
I went to see <i>Lilies of</i>
<i>the Field</i> last night.

00:06.552 --> 00:07.759
I'm reading the book right now.

00:07.892 --> 00:10.921
Sidney Poitier's performance
was... fabulous.

00:11.065 --> 00:13.498
I'm right at the part where he's
starting to build the chapel.

00:13.599 --> 00:15.594
Oh, I won't ruin it for you, then.

00:17.678 --> 00:18.891
Good morning.

00:19.043 --> 00:20.880
Good morning, Sister.

00:22.000 --> 00:28.074
